text: Liz Miles (born January 25, 1955) is an American rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Fresno, California
